## ▶️ Getting Started
**Prerequisites**
- Java 17+
- Maven
- PostgreSQL (optional if using H2)

**Run locally**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/ecoroute-optimizer.git
cd ecoroute-optimizer
mvn spring-boot:run
